{
  "stem": "19441.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and when I saw it-- and I was in charge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went and I said, how could I help that situation?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to the end of the camp, and I found out that there are some clay which is similar like making bricks from.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and because they were strong woman, the Polish-- it was in the beginning, but some caught the sickness very quickly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, [INAUDIBLE], Stasja, [INAUDIBLE]-- what their names were-- we are going to do something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are going to disinfect the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because when the sun came up, and all that excrement was there, so that stank hell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also that brings bacteria, and inside too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I arranged that, because I, I tell you what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I, I don't know how I could, but I, I did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I stopped there a man who brought things for the commandant woman with the horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I said, tomorrow you are going to bring me whitewash, two barrels of whitewash.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What do you think?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Two barrels?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Where do I take?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't care where you take, but bring me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But how could I bring you, because I carry that to the commandant woman?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You will [POINTS] put the barrels here, and we will be waiting for you and we will quickly take the barrels away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If they catch me, [POINTING] I am responsible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you, I don't know where he got the whitewash, but he brought two barrels of whitewash.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I brought the earth from the back of the camp, and at night with the girls-- because workers have been always there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a ladder, there was a stick, there was a, a bucket.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
